?CND40:	CALL	NOUN-USED?,CH-RHYMER,W?RHYMER
	ZERO?	STACK /?CCL45
	CALL	ADJ-USED?,CH-RHYMER,W?THOMAS
	ZERO?	STACK /?CCL45
